117
00:07:12,083 --> 00:07:15,083
Oooh...! Kyouma's
going out on a date?

118
00:07:15,166 --> 00:07:18,708
That's interesting... Here's
your iced coffee, Meow-ster...

119
00:07:18,791 --> 00:07:21,750
Now, surely we're close
enough to tell me who with...

120
00:07:21,833 --> 00:07:24,333
