It's patently obvious...

121
00:07:24,416 --> 00:07:27,000
I do not foul my own nest.

122
00:07:27,083 --> 00:07:29,583
Mind if I make an
observation, Casanova sir...?

123
00:07:29,666 --> 00:07:31,875
All this woman-chasing
is going to play havoc

124
00:07:31,958 --> 00:07:33,208
with your special technique.

125
00:07:33,291 --> 00:07:36,375
What does she mean
"all this woman-chasing?"

126
00:07:36,458 --> 00:07:39,666
Hey! You can't leave
loaded statements

127
00:07:39,750 --> 00:07:41,375
like that just
hanging in the air!

128
00:07:45,875 --> 00:07:48,750
So... a special
technique, huh...?

129
00:07:48,833 --> 00:07:52,083
I bet Ruka would love to
see what that's all about.

130
00:07:53,666 --> 00:07:55,416
Wait, that came out wrong...

131
00:07:55,500 --> 00:07:58,083
I was aiming that
at your alter ego...!

132
00:07:58,166 --> 00:08:00,500
Well neither of us is amused
by your lewd insinuation...

133
00:08:00,583 --> 00:08:02,458
Filthy assistant.

134
00:08:02,541 --> 00:08:04,416
What...? Are you serious?

135
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:06,208
Wow, thanks for
making this awkward...

136
00:08:06,291 --> 00:08:08,375
Look, she brought up
your special technique...

137
00:08:08,458 --> 00:08:10,333
I was just pointing out
how stupid it sounded...

138
00:08:10,416 --> 00:08:13,208
I wasn't... trying
to be all perverted.

139
00:08:13,291 --> 00:08:14,375
You look like a radish.

140
00:08:14,458 --> 00:08:15,833
Oh shut up...!

141
00:08:15,916 --> 00:08:18,208
I'm blushing 'cause I know
your mind is in the gutter.

142
00:08:18,291 --> 00:08:20,125
Point is, just go
on the damn date!

143
00:08:20,208 --> 00:08:21,291
Why do you think we're having

144
00:08:21,375 --> 00:08:23,166
this awkward conversation
to begin with?!

145
00:08:23,250 --> 00:08:26,083
Okarin...

146
00:08:26,166 --> 00:08:27,916
There some special
reason you were waitin'

147
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:30,583
