help me on a real tête-à-tête.

155
00:08:49,625 --> 00:08:52,125
First things first, I need
to find somewhere popular...

156
00:08:52,208 --> 00:08:55,250
Aoyama, perhaps...
Or Nishi-Azabu...

157
00:08:55,333 --> 00:08:56,875
"Fashionable and trendy...

158
