is alien to me...

160
00:09:04,333 --> 00:09:08,083
How can a Martian be expected
to navigate the oceans of Venus?

161
00:09:08,166 --> 00:09:09,791
Better steel yourself, capt'n.

162
00:09:09,875 --> 00:09:11,041
Bite your tongue...!

163
00:09:11,125 --> 00:09:13,375
My IQ is on par
with Sir Isaac Newton.

164
00:09:13,458 --> 00:09:15,958
And like his august self I have
no use for the fairer sex...

165
00:09:16,041 --> 00:09:19,083
