you're experienced...?!

170
00:09:27,541 --> 00:09:30,291
Pray tell how many wayward ships
have you coerced into your port?

171
00:09:30,375 --> 00:09:32,833
Go on, I'm listening!

172
00:09:32,916 --> 00:09:34,208
Just as I thought!

173
00:09:34,291 --> 00:09:36,416
You're no less chaste
than the rest of us seekers;

174
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:39,250
ergo utterly devoid of
input on the topic at hand!

175
00:09:39,333 --> 00:09:41,041
Not that I'd expect otherwise.

176
00:09:41,125 --> 00:09:44,291
Fine! So I've never gone
all the way! Screw you!

177
00:09:49,208 --> 00:09:51,666
"The key to making your
first date the first of many

178
