wearing a lab coat...

184
00:10:06,041 --> 00:10:08,416
"Where you choose to dine
is equally important...

185
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:10,250
However, don't feel
you have to pick

186
00:10:10,333 --> 00:10:11,833
