187
00:10:11,916 --> 00:10:14,791
Usually the ideal restaurant
is one you already frequent."

188
00:10:14,875 --> 00:10:17,916
Ah, well in that case...
There's always here.

189
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,916
That's not what
they're saying, tool...!

190
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,416
A ramshackle greasy
spoon like this

191
