and dine a girl!

192
00:10:23,125 --> 00:10:26,708
Okay... That only leaves
one option... Queen May's.

193
00:10:26,791 --> 00:10:30,000
In what universe
is that acceptable?!

194
00:10:30,083 --> 00:10:31,166
Then a weapon shop?

195
00:10:31,250 --> 00:10:32,708
You gonna club her
over the head?!

196
00:10:33,708 --> 00:10:35,958
Will you pry yourself from
the twaddle in that book

197
00:10:36,041 --> 00:10:38,041
