How would you know?!

201
00:10:43,791 --> 00:10:44,833
I'm going to punch
you in the face.

202
00:10:44,916 --> 00:10:46,458
Excuse me...
Have you considered

203
00:10:46,541 --> 00:10:48,708
giving the wisdom between
these pages a try?

204
00:10:48,791 --> 00:10:50,875
