strategy guide, jackass!

205
00:10:50,958 --> 00:10:54,416
So...?! You don't think dating
is a giant part of that scene?!

206
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:56,666
Where do you think I learned
the best way to hold hands...?

207
00:10:56,750 --> 00:10:59,625
The trick is to position your
arm so that a strategically

208
00:10:59,708 --> 00:11:01,583
