first glimmer of a plan...

215
00:11:16,875 --> 00:11:19,000
Stop feeling sorry for
yourself and put it on.

216
00:11:19,666 --> 00:11:21,291
Take the tags off;
you're not a mannequin.

217
00:11:21,375 --> 00:11:24,083
And oh my god, have
you never worn a tie?

218
00:11:24,166 --> 00:11:26,958
Seriously... Why am I even
bothering with this...?

219
00:11:27,041 --> 00:11:28,458
Aright then.

220
00:11:28,541 --> 00:11:31,500
