rattling around in yours?

229
00:11:46,791 --> 00:11:48,958
Uh! Stay focused...!

230
00:11:49,041 --> 00:11:51,291
A gentleman spreads his
handkerchief out on a park bench

231
00:11:51,375 --> 00:11:54,041
